        <h2 id="examples">Real GBP optimization examples</h2>
        <p>Three case studies from our 2025-2026 audit portfolio, each showing what a specific optimization move actually delivered.</p>

        <h3>1. Miami accounting firm — category + photos + reviews</h3>
        <p>Started with only name, address, and phone. Added the primary category "Certified Public Accountant" plus four secondary categories, uploaded 15 photos, wrote a keyword-informed description, and launched a review request campaign. Moved into the Local Pack top 3 for "accountant in Miami" within 10 weeks.</p>

